(Common Mistakes) Tj
T*
(- Misunderstanding the core focus of Nuclear Physics: decay, radiation types, and) Tj
T*
(nuclear stability.) Tj
T*
(- Confusing nuclear changes with chemical reactions.) Tj
T*
(- Jumping to an answer without showing the steps or reasoning clearly.) Tj
T*
(- Practising Nuclear Physics without checking whether the method matches the question) Tj
T*
(being asked.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Study Tips) Tj
T*
(- Rewrite the overview of Nuclear Physics in your own words after studying it.) Tj
T*
(- Use short exercises built around radioactivity and decay questions before trying) Tj
T*
(harder tasks.) Tj
T*
